---
title: Crispy Eggplant over Penne Marinara with Mozzarella & Italian Herbs
description: Classic Italian restaurant vibes abound in this impressive meal. You'll fry breaded eggplant slices until crisp and golden brown, then top with a crown of melty mozzarella and serve atop tangy-savory penne marinara. You may want to break out the red-checkered tablecloth and candlesticks, because this hearty dish deserves them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2f71da27a53fcaa21f46e-3f5c501d.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67b2f71da27a53fcaa21f46e-en-US.pdf
